thread.title: Canada bombing injures 15, two suspects flee

title: Canada bombing injures 15, two suspects flee
text:
Canada bombing injures 15, two suspects flee 9:04am BST - 00:54
Authorities say 15 people have been wounded, with several critically injured, after two unidentified men set off a bomb inside a restaurant about 20 miles west of Toronto. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
